"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The president of the European Commission, Ursula von der Leyen, suggested using frozen Russian assets to buy weapons for Ukraine. The EU has over \u20ac200bn of Russian assets frozen, but there are concerns about Russian retaliation.\",            \"english_title\": \"European Union and Ukraine\",            \"translated_version\": \"La presidenta de la Comisi\u00f3n Europea, Ursula von der Leyen, sugiri\u00f3 usar activos rusos congelados para comprar armas para Ucrania. La UE tiene m\u00e1s de \u20ac200bn de activos rusos congelados, pero hay preocupaciones sobre la represalia rusa.\",            \"translated_title\": \"European Union and Ukraine\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Mitch McConnell, the Republican leader in the US Senate, will step down in November. He has been a strong supporter of Ukraine and faced opposition within his party on aiding the country.\",            \"english_title\": \"American Politics\",            \"translated_version\": \"Mitch McConnell, el l\u00edder republicano en el Senado de EE. UU., renunciar\u00e1 en noviembre. Ha sido un fuerte partidario de Ucrania y enfrent\u00f3 oposici\u00f3n dentro de su partido para ayudar al pa\u00eds.\",            \"translated_title\": \"American Politics\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Apple has decided to end its electric car project after a decade of development and significant investment. The project was seen as ambitious, but a commercially available autonomous vehicle was still far off.\",            \"english_title\": \"Technology News\",            \"translated_version\": \"Apple ha decidido terminar su proyecto de coche el\u00e9ctrico despu\u00e9s de una d\u00e9cada de desarrollo e inversi\u00f3n significativa. El proyecto se consideraba ambicioso, pero un veh\u00edculo aut\u00f3nomo disponible comercialmente a\u00fan estaba lejos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Technology News\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Alexei Navalny, a prominent Russian opposition leader who passed away in a penal colony, will be buried in Moscow. His team faced obstacles in holding the funeral due to political events in Russia.\",            \"english_title\": \"Russian Politics\",            \"translated_version\": \"Alexei Navalny, un prominente l\u00edder opositor ruso que falleci\u00f3 en una colonia penal, ser\u00e1 enterrado en Mosc\u00fa. Su equipo enfrent\u00f3 obst\u00e1culos para celebrar el funeral debido a eventos pol\u00edticos en Rusia.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Russian Politics\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Asylum applications to the EU increased by 18% in 2023, reaching levels not seen since the migration crisis of 2015-16. Germany received a significant number of applications, with Syrians, Afghans, and Palestinians among the top applicants.\",            \"english_title\": \"Global Migration Trends\",            \"translated_version\": \"Las solicitudes de asilo a la UE aumentaron un 18% en 2023, alcanzando niveles no vistos desde la crisis migratoria de 2015-16. Alemania recibi\u00f3 un n\u00famero significativo de solicitudes, con sirios, afganos y palestinos entre los principales solicitantes.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Global Migration Trends\"        }    ]}"